{"tid":1646513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地一定要贏。。。先對得住死去嘅手足。。","createTime":"2019-10-11T10:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T16:33:34.000Z","uid":179859,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"efaf7c33090d9e6a91a8fdbdcef3396420b19df2","tid":1646513,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"6月開始「反送中」爆發<br />\n我只會定義佢為一場「運動」<br />\n<br />\n慢慢地<br />\n政府對我地嘅漠視 唔理會<br />\n再加埋種種從來無人預計過嘅因素<br />\n警察變成黑警 濫暴 濫權 性侵 強姦雞姦輪姦 殺人 棄屍<br />\n同時警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n呢場「革命」<br />\n已經返唔到轉頭喇<br />\n<br />\n我地無辦法<br />\n比返安穩嘅生活一啲為左我地而被捕嘅前線<br />\n我地無辦法<br />\n比返健康嘅身體一啲為左我地而傷殘嘅手足<br />\n我地無辦法<br />\n比返條命為左我地而犧牲嘅義士<br />\n<br />\n我地呢一刻可以做嘅<br />\n除左為佢地查清楚成件事來龍去脈之外<br />\n就係要努力埋佢地果份<br />\n我地只有「贏」<br />\n先可以<br />\n令佢地大大少少嘅犧牲變得有意義<br />\n抖夠喇香港人<br />\n一齊再努力啦好嗎？<br />\n兩個月前我地團火絕對唔可以熄<br />\n至少<br />\n係贏之前 唔可以熄。"},{"pid":"b2c7b28c04d7fa08a7ecb29279ee27518b6bf1a3","tid":1646513,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"1/50"},{"pid":"c6f6b7b42f20dd81e6e6bb232c35684fc6907f12","tid":1646513,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"2/50"},{"pid":"5abc1d1c336e11146f7d2c934a04b10323d526dd","tid":1646513,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c140794507b95e00f49076b9e2dd84d68929fb7d","tid":1646513,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"a650eb4131299918ce412c2e60a5b8f1f5d4fd57","tid":1646513,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"d2cc7e63ae955d782aa07a0a0c5b92715f65a00a","tid":1646513,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:29:02.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"3b510d63cf8c4b75843e267bc9b7c00f44e2a255","tid":1646513,"uid":179859,"like":0,"dislike"